      <title>特朗普团队正寻求放宽美国自动驾驶汽车规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/trump-team-said-to-want-to-ease-us-rules-for-self-driving-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的过渡团队成员告诉顾问，他们计划将完全自动驾驶汽车的联邦框架作为交通部的优先事项之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/trump-team-said-to-want-to-ease-us-rules-for-self-driving-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 20:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果公司的蒂姆·库克有办法应对迫在眉睫的特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-11-17/how-will-president-donald-trump-s-new-tariffs-affect-apple-products-and-prices-m3lnfx64</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于严重依赖中国，苹果仍然容易受到唐纳德·特朗普关税的影响。但蒂姆·库克可能有计划减轻打击。此外：详细介绍了苹果即将推出的智能家居设备，该公司在 AirTags 的首次硬件升级方面取得了进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-11-17/how-will-president-donald-trump-s-new-tariffs-affect-apple-products-and-prices-m3lnfx64</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 13:45:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
